78
00:05:15,083 --> 00:05:16,958
It's good to see
you again, Momo.

79
00:05:17,041 --> 00:05:18,416
Remember me?

80
00:05:18,500 --> 00:05:20,875
I'm the girl who gave you
the eraser during the exam.

81
00:05:20,958 --> 00:05:22,208
[chuckles]

82
00:05:22,291 --> 00:05:25,750
[MOMO] I hadn't felt that
happy in a long time.

83
00:05:25,833 --> 00:05:28,083
Ugh... I should have
noticed back then.

84
00:05:28,166 --> 00:05:30,125
