making some sense?!

155
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:39,125
How about this: You haven't
seen Toji in a while,

156
00:08:39,208 --> 00:08:41,583
so why don't you start off
with a simple apology.

157
00:08:41,666 --> 00:08:42,625
