235
00:11:47,541 --> 00:11:49,791
[MOMO gasps, screams]

236
00:11:49,875 --> 00:11:50,958
[gasps]

237
00:11:55,125 --> 00:11:57,083
--[SAE gasps]
--I can't bear to watch!

238
00:12:09,666 --> 00:12:10,708
[KAIRI sighs]

239
00:12:12,666 --> 00:12:14,833
[PATIENTS clapping]

240
00:12:14,916 --> 00:12:18,291
I have never seen
such a heroic act.

241
00:12:18,375 --> 00:12:20,583
[MALE PATIENT]
I'm so glad you didn't fall.

242
00:12:20,666 --> 00:12:23,583
--[SAE growls]
